{"tid":1569184,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再飲喜茶上連登呀仆街仔！","createTime":"2019-09-14T13:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T16:41:12.000Z","uid":8361,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab74e7db925ef92bc07a5e140afff081a84d068","tid":1569184,"uid":8361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母</span><br />\n係咪唔飲大陸野唔食大陸野會死呀你老味！<br />\n見到你班仆街睇住連登排隊等喜茶食海底撈就火都黎！<br />\n控制下你把閪口係唔係咁難呀？<br />\n光復香港呀屌你老母！<br />\n幫襯大陸野你好唔好意思話自己係連登仔？<br />\n咁多野俾你選擇  你係都要食大陸野<br />\n<br />\n唔使諗住屌鳩我自由乜乜乜<br />\n香港係有自由俾你選擇你嘅食物<br />\n但係我話俾你知你唔撚配做連登仔呀！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大陸狗！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"af82e8894c65dde3c4efd6e3755ba3866a4d0ece","tid":1569184,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:49:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d2e54543906116381898aa0847b166de6480840","tid":1569184,"uid":308706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，我唔會飲屎水嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a067ce3a16b55c031f152d40b132d07c1c65d357","tid":1569184,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:51:25.000Z","msg":"正視聽post 需要手足推同討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不再推未Fact Check 嘅內容<br />\n不指責，盡量做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔該大大力推91